    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Black Light Kills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在一个被神秘失踪所震撼的小镇上，艾登发现自己踏上了一段噩梦般的旅程。失去对现实的掌控，他必须面对可怕的生物，并揭开神秘事件的真相。答案埋藏在可怕的秘密之中。</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>   游戏特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两种不同的结局在等待你: </strong>根据你在游戏过程中经历的事件，故事可能会有两种不同的结局。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模糊的故事线：</strong> 艾登的心理动荡将把你带入一个深刻的叙事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寒冷的氛围：</strong> 这个安静却令人不安的小镇将随着每一步让你更接近疯狂的边缘。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>线索：</strong> 仔细检查每一个细节，以揭示小镇的黑暗秘密。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/e63c3efc3a83d0beae9d02db1120af6f.poster.avif?t=1745231765\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/e63c3efc3a83d0beae9d02db1120af6f.webm?t=1745231765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/e63c3efc3a83d0beae9d02db1120af6f.mp4?t=1745231765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理崩溃的敏感性：</strong> 随着环境变化，艾登的心理恶化加深，使你不断质疑现实的本质。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人注目的声音和视觉设计：</strong> 气氛音效和黑暗视觉效果将确保每一步都充满紧张和恐惧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理紧张：</strong> 隐藏的危险和心理游戏将导致艾登质疑自己的理智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/21dd3cea4cd24540f3b30c7c3335fc21.poster.avif?t=1745231765\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/21dd3cea4cd24540f3b30c7c3335fc21.webm?t=1745231765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/21dd3cea4cd24540f3b30c7c3335fc21.mp4?t=1745231765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扭曲思维的体验：</strong> 期待遭遇使人迷惑的事件和幻觉视野，挑战你对现实的感知。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式音景：</strong> 游戏拥有精心制作的声音设计，增强心理恐怖体验，使你保持紧张。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>孤独和隔离：</strong> 荒凉的走廊和废弃的房间加深了孤独感和隔离感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/75b3c824f4825a73d52e94c549053df1.poster.avif?t=1745231765\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/75b3c824f4825a73d52e94c549053df1.webm?t=1745231765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177550/extras/75b3c824f4825a73d52e94c549053df1.mp4?t=1745231765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐惧不仅在外面，还潜伏在艾登的内心。你准备好踏上这段旅程了吗？</strong></p></li></ul>",
